alerts.description:
There is a risk of storm-force gusts (level 2 of 4).
Height range: > 1000 m; Max. gusts: 75-95 km/h; Wind direction: south-west then west; Increased gusts: near showers and in exposed locations < 110 km/h

There is a risk of gale-force gusts (level 2 of 4).
Height range: > 600 m; Max. gusts: 65-80 km/h; Wind direction: south-west then west; Increased gusts: near showers and in exposed locations < 95 km/h

There is a risk of wind gusts (level 1 of 4).
Max. gusts: ~ 60 km/h; Wind direction: south-west then west; Increased gusts: near showers and in exposed locations ~ 70 km/h
